## Limitations

The findings presented in this report are based on available data and research, which may not capture all aspects of the complex relationship between gender and crime. Additionally, cultural and regional differences can influence crime rates and gender roles, which are not fully addressed in this report. Further research is needed to explore these nuances and develop comprehensive strategies to reduce crime across genders.

